  "body": "<center><img alt=\"Simple Banhammer\" src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/sGuB2CEM/images/0bbebcc068777d402917200ee44b0e41a3e62ed7.png\"></center>\n\n## Description\nThis pack adds model banhammer for diamond/netherite axes.\n\n## Installing\nThe resource pack must be placed in the resourcepacks folder in the .minecraft directory\n\nDefault: \n* Windows: **C:\\\\Users\\\\%USERNAME%\\\\AppData\\\\Roaming\\\\.minecraft\\\\resourcepacks\\\\**\n* Linux: **~/.minecraft/resourcepacks**\n\nNext, in Minecraft, go to **[Settings]** -> **[Resource Packs]** -> Select the desired pack -> **[Done]**\n\n## Requirements\n* Minecraft version above **1.14**\n* Installed [OptiFine](https://optifine.net/downloads) (If you using Forge)\n* Installed [CIT Resewn](https://modrinth.com/mod/cit-resewn) (If you using Fabric)\n\n## Feedback\nYou can contact us via [email](mailto:mystyhaddock355@ya.ru) or [Discord](https://discord.com/users/817075264567115806).\n\n## Finance support\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/bZTgH6Lk/images/e6ee8090f49140f4bb1ba886d26c795ced9a79ad.png\" width=160 heght=48></img>\n```\nTGjiLho2eUMRAMPf6PUZs16EF2cvphnv8d\n```\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/bZTgH6Lk/images/1fa354a88c1846b75d48d6a8988e0731a5271251.png\" width=160 heght=48></img>\n```\n1dvL4mQf7cMmXhLc3A2tiyymVDF19TJnV\n```\n\nor USDC-Polygon:\n```\n0x390a54d13f62d62b4ee366aa23d4b0e0244c496f\n```\n\n## My (our) projects\n\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/giac\" title=\"GUI Icons as Cells\"><img src=\"https://cdn-raw.modrinth.com/data/OPyn7IN9/28b201026d565cd5ca45426ab73ede6ef707eba9.png\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></img></a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/totems_o_players\" title=\"Totems'o'players\"><img src=\"https://cdn-raw.modrinth.com/data/lhXx6Sw8/524d5de9d0f8b6b8cd4f5731f1a376487e7f99ff.png\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></img></a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/alt-swords-classic\" title=\"Alt-Swords Classic\"><img src=\"https://cdn-raw.modrinth.com/data/OYHTUzqk/3ff31c40daf54682cccbc41c26ab7de27c1eefd1.png\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></img></a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/bettertoolposition\" title=\"BetterToolPosition\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/bZTgH6Lk/8b7bdc707522ffe3dba0e329d543e24689ea851d.png\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></img></a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/alt-swords\" title=\"Alt-Swords\"><img src=\"https://cdn-raw.modrinth.com/data/b3wxEHWx/184afd4e15db29981dca7c28a5bdcfa57fd8a918.png\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></img></a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/totems_o_players_3d\" title=\"Totems'o'players 3D\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/FFNNbNu2/7d21c5a2e03f198a18ef02900636bf9c0c6d5c2d.png\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></img></a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/firefighter_kit\" title=\"Firefighter Kit\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/6c0f0EHL/c3e2e827512048cbe4818714772a4c2f320bfe2f.png\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></img></a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/project/create-weapon-pack\" title=\"Create: Weapon Pack\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/WYqq2oLg/7dec424352ef6f5d14dea154230b516aea667201.png\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></img></a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/ccwp\" title=\"Create: Weapon Pack\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/KoK8Rd39/9bae7392e8ca1c5b739d1e3cefbe7c0310364f3d.png\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></img></a>",
